PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>

SELECT ( ( ?maxPop2022 - ?pop2010 ) / ?pop2010 * 100 AS ?growthPercentage ) ( ( ?maxPop2022 - ?pop2010 ) / ?pop2010 * 100 >= 1 AS ?atLeastOnePercent ) WHERE {
  SELECT ( MAX( ?pop2022 ) AS ?maxPop2022 ) ?pop2010 WHERE {
    wd:Q183 p:P1082 ?popStatement2010 .
    ?popStatement2010 ps:P1082 ?pop2010 .
    ?popStatement2010 pq:P585 ?date2010 .
    FILTER ( YEAR( ?date2010 ) = 2010 ) wd:Q183 p:P1082 ?popStatement2022 .
    ?popStatement2022 ps:P1082 ?pop2022 .
    ?popStatement2022 pq:P585 ?date2022 .
    FILTER ( YEAR( ?date2022 ) = 2022 )
  }
  GROUP BY ?pop2010
}
